ocal stability,\nnon-oscillatory convergence and the rate of convergence of the CCFM. Further,\nto better understand the oscillations in the system dynamics, we characterize\nthe type of the Hopf bifurcation and the asymptotic orbital stability of the\nlimit cycles using Poincare normal forms and the center manifold theory. The\nanalysis is complemented with stability charts, bifurcation diagrams and MATLAB\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2016 12:22:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2016 09:08:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2017 14:40:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 29 Oct 2017 17:07:14 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2018 06:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-28"}
